high_descs: Turn right and walk to the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap laying on the side of the bath tub.
Move to your left and face the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub.
Turn around and walk toward the door, then turn left to face the cabinet.
Pick up the bar of soap laying on the cabinet.
Turn around and walk back to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub next to the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the tub, turn to the right and go forward.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the edge of the tub.
Turn around and move forward, turn to the right to face the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub.
Turn around and cross the room, turn to the right and go to the table that is to the right of the garbage can.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the table.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the bath tub.
Pick up the soap on the right side of the tub.
Go to the middle of the tub.
Put the soap in the tub.
Turn around and go to the cabinet with the tissues.
Pick up the soap on the cabinet.
Turn right and go back to the tub.
Put the soap in the tub to the right of the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Put bars of soap in the tub.
